Sub-policy 4
https://www.thebicestercollection.com/en/legal/cookie-consent:
This app works best with JavaScript enabled.
Cookie Policy
What are cookies?
Cookies are small files that are stored on your computer's hard drive when you visit a website.
What do cookies do?
Cookies do lots of different jobs, such as letting you navigate between pages efficiently and enhancing the customer's experience when visiting a website. For example they can remember your preferences.
Yes, cookies are small text files. They can't look into your computer or read any personal information.
Cookies can't carry viruses or install anything harmful on your computer.
Are cookies used for tracking?
Yes, we also use cookies to track how many people are visiting our website and also which areas of the site they are viewing. This gives us an insight into how our customers are using our website and helps us to improve usability.
What types of cookies are used?
We use a number of cookies; these are session cookies and persistent cookies. These cookies do not collect personal information.
Session Cookies
These cookies identify that the user is moving from page to page and terminate when the user stops visiting the various pages. It is then deleted when the browser is closed.
Persistent Cookies
These cookies help us to remember your settings when you revisit our website and therefore these continue to stay on your computer after you have visited our site.
Third Party Cookies
All cookies belong to an owner such as advertising partners and can also be set into external content from third party websites within our website.
Should I keep cookies switched on?
We would like you to keep cookies 'turned on' while you visit our websites so you receive the best possible experience.
However if you would like to turn off cookies you can do so by editing the settings in your browser.
Turn off cookies in Internet Explorer
Turn off cookies in Chrome
Turn off cookies in Safari
Turn off cookies in FireFox
Turn off cookies in Safari iOS
Turn off cookies in Google Android
By using this website you are confirming you are happy to accept the use of cookies.
About Cookies On This Site
The Bicester Collection™ use cookies to provide you with personalised content, deliver targeted advertising and to analyse visitors to our website. For more information, see our
Privacy Policy
To find out further information about the cookies we use select Options.
